<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rapport Statistique Promotions</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif; color: #2c3e50; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #F7B731; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .row { display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .col { display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; background: #fdfdfd; }
        .kpi-row { display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .kpi-box { display: table-cell; width: 25%; text-align: center; padding: 15px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #edf2f7; border-radius: 10px; }
        .kpi-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #4F46E5; }
        .kpi-label { font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 5px; }
        h3 { font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 0; }
        .chart-img { max-width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
        table th, table td { border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
        table th { background: #f8fafc; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>Rapport Analytique RE7LA</h1>
    <p>Statistiques des Promotions - {{ "now"|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
</div>

<div class="kpi-row">
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalPromos }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Total Promos</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalReservations }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Réservations</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalViews }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Total Vues</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ engagementRate }}%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Engagement</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Distribution par Type</h3>
            <img src="{{ pieChartUrl }}" class="chart-img">
            <p style="font-size:11px; color:#64748b; margin-top:10px;">
                Individuelles: {{ nbIndiv }} | Packs: {{ nbPacks }}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Répartition par Catégorie</h3>
            <img src="{{ doughnutChartUrl }}" class="chart-img">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col" style="width: 100%; display: block;">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 10 Performance (Réservations)</h3>
            <img src="{{ barChartUrl }}" class="chart-img" style="width: 100%;">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>💎 Clients les plus actifs</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>Utilisateur</th><th>Réservations</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for email, count in topUsers %}
                    <tr><td>{{ email }}</td><td>{{ count }}</td></tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card" style="border: 1px dashed #e74c3c;">
            <h3>⚠️ Analyse de l'offre</h3>
            <p style="font-size:12px; line-height:1.6;">
                L'engagement moyen est de {{ engagementRate }}%. Les promotions de type pack représentent {{ (nbPacks / totalPromos * 100)|round }}% du catalogue. 
                Une augmentation des réservations est observée sur les offres à forte tendance.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
